item.title: NNSI: Northern Nomad Systems Integration Final Report
item.description: The Northern Nomad Systems Integration (NNSI) project has ended, and the final report has been submitted to the supervising professor and second reader. The project did not warrant a Github page. Instead, I have made the final report available for reading here, or for download here. Any questions about the project can be directed to me at zeinhajjali@outlook.com.

item.title: GSBR: Gyroscope Self-Balancing Robot Final Report
item.description: The Gyroscope Self-Balancing Robot (GSBR) project has ended. Previous posts on the progress and results can be found on this site. A more detailed and better edited look at the project can be found in the final report that the team has written up here or as a download here. The source code and testing code can all be found at the Github page here.
